Dialogue: 1,1:20:53.40,1:20:58.04,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4}喝了热茶后
Dialogue: 1,1:20:58.04,1:21:02.51,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4}荒原凉风阵阵
Dialogue: 1,1:21:02.51,1:21:09.28,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4}从丘上俯视的世界
Dialogue: 1,1:21:09.28,1:21:11.28,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4}是我的世界
Dialogue: 1,1:21:11.28,1:21:16.06,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4}清甜泉水涌出
Dialogue: 1,1:21:16.06,1:21:20.43,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4}赤足戏水
Dialogue: 1,1:21:20.43,1:21:27.30,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4}同从前没任何变化
